WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:02.336
<i>[metallic thump]</i>

00:05.464 --> 00:08.425
<i>[intense music]</i>

00:08.425 --> 00:15.224
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:15.224 --> 00:18.393
- My name's Matthew Berry.
I'm 55 years old.

00:18.393 --> 00:22.856
